OL,10,     Fsprings a leak, causing trouble
OL,11,     Ffor the Naughty Lass.
OL,12,G2100 Operation Gold Rush
OL,13,     FDigging for Gold: The team arrives
OL,14,     Fat Dawson City and sets up a
OL,15,     Fmining camp in the gold fields -
OL,16,     Fbut they have just five days to
OL,17,     Ffind gold using only traditional
OL,18,     F19th-century methods.
